description: This file defines a mock class 'rtArrayObjectMock' for unit testing, which inherits from 'rtArrayObjectImpl' and uses Google Mock to mock methods 'pushBack'. It is used for testing components that interact with 'rtArrayObject' objects in the codebase.

classes.name: rtArrayObjectMock
classes.description: Mock class for 'rtArrayObject' interface used in testing, providing mock implementations of 'pushBack' methods.

methods.name: pushBack (const char* v)
methods.description: Mock method to simulate adding a string value to the array object.

methods.name: pushBack (rtValue v)
methods.description: Mock method to simulate adding an 'rtValue' object to the array object.
